WEBVTT

00:14.040 --> 00:16.700
I've never thought
that the legendary prodigy,

00:16.710 --> 00:18.670
Young Master Zhuge
of Great Yong's Zhuge family,

00:18.670 --> 00:20.070
would fall to this point.

00:20.550 --> 00:20.870
Wasn't he

00:20.870 --> 00:22.670
the most feared spy master?

00:23.440 --> 00:25.440
How could he end up so badly wounded?

00:29.670 --> 00:30.390
Xing,

00:31.120 --> 00:32.850
I know you have many questions,

00:33.240 --> 00:35.390
and I should give you some explanation.

00:35.390 --> 00:36.920
But I have my reasons not to.

00:37.280 --> 00:39.140
Wait for me to settle everything.

00:44.520 --> 00:45.390
Zhuge Yue,

00:46.560 --> 00:48.200
can you stay for me?

00:51.430 --> 00:52.070
Yes.

00:52.430 --> 00:53.430
You're right.

00:55.030 --> 00:56.470
But this is my business.

00:56.920 --> 00:58.520
It has nothing to do with you.

01:13.710 --> 01:16.400
I didn't even notice
your forbearance and pain.

01:17.120 --> 01:18.950
And I've been resenting and blaming you

01:18.950 --> 01:19.750
all this time,

01:20.070 --> 01:21.510
never once thinking about

01:21.510 --> 01:23.590
how much hardship you've endured.

01:23.640 --> 01:25.310
If he intended not to tell you,

01:25.310 --> 01:26.510
fearing you'd worry,

01:26.880 --> 01:28.539
you naturally wouldn't know.

01:43.740 --> 01:45.430
This poison in him is very strange,

01:45.430 --> 01:47.280
twisting along his heart meridians
and limbs,

01:47.280 --> 01:48.479
yet it moves like thread.

01:48.479 --> 01:50.789
I've tried my best but couldn't remove it.

01:50.789 --> 01:53.000
For now, I can only use needles
to seal his acupoints

01:53.000 --> 01:54.789
to protect his organs,

01:55.789 --> 01:57.229
but how long this will hold

01:57.229 --> 01:58.710
depends on his own strength.

01:58.710 --> 01:59.430
Your Highness,

01:59.430 --> 02:01.000
what should we do with our plan

02:01.000 --> 02:02.070
to rescue General He?

02:02.070 --> 02:03.670
We don't have much time left.

02:04.200 --> 02:05.120
At this point,

02:05.790 --> 02:06.950
we can only wait for He Xiao

02:06.950 --> 02:08.520
to be handed over to the Black Eagle Army

02:08.520 --> 02:12.210
and look for an opportunity
when they're on the way back to Great Yan.

02:12.210 --> 02:15.940
Tomorrow, I'll go with Fang Miaomiao
to gather information first.

03:35.770 --> 03:40.950
[REBIRTH]

03:41.620 --> 03:44.010
[Episode 15]

03:44.040 --> 03:44.960
[Lincheng]

03:56.430 --> 03:58.030
Once the Yong Army opens the gate,

03:58.030 --> 04:01.030
and the Great Yan prisoners of war
walk out through it,

04:01.150 --> 04:02.410
we'll be able to locate

04:02.840 --> 04:03.870
He Xiao.

04:04.520 --> 04:05.680
Open the gate!

04:40.860 --> 04:41.790
They're coming.

04:48.880 --> 04:49.510
He Xiao!

04:53.330 --> 04:54.840
Oh no, it's a trap!

04:55.040 --> 04:56.170
Close the city gate!

04:56.850 --> 04:57.380
Hurry!

05:05.950 --> 05:07.040
Charge!

05:13.680 --> 05:14.740
What's that sound?

05:15.040 --> 05:15.950
Something must have happened.

05:15.950 --> 05:17.410
Don't get up. I'll go help.

05:58.990 --> 05:59.830
[He Xiao, General of Xiuli Army]

05:59.260 --> 06:00.060
General Chu!

06:03.140 --> 06:03.820
Get on the horse!

06:03.820 --> 06:04.380
Yes!

06:05.510 --> 06:06.630
Stop those three!

06:07.110 --> 06:08.520
Don't let them escape!

06:26.510 --> 06:28.160
He Xiao, Miaomiao, you go first!

06:28.160 --> 06:28.680
I'll cover you!

06:28.680 --> 06:29.630
My Lord, you can't do that!

06:29.630 --> 06:30.360
It's an order!

06:30.360 --> 06:30.950
Your Highness!

06:30.950 --> 06:31.510
Go!

07:40.870 --> 07:41.510
Run!

07:58.870 --> 07:59.480
Run!

07:59.480 --> 08:01.360
Young Master! Young Master!

08:01.830 --> 08:02.750
Young Master!

08:04.350 --> 08:05.050
Young Master,

08:05.050 --> 08:07.020
it's me, Shiyi!

08:05.480 --> 08:06.940
[Yue Shiyi, Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor]

08:07.160 --> 08:07.830
Shiyi?

08:08.870 --> 08:09.670
Young Master.

08:10.430 --> 08:11.080
Shiyi.

08:12.780 --> 08:13.980
Why are you guys here?

08:33.549 --> 08:34.270
Chu.

08:42.200 --> 08:42.870
Chu.

08:44.630 --> 08:45.630
Come back with me.

08:46.440 --> 08:47.900
Let's go back to Great Yan.

08:48.030 --> 08:48.720
Yan Xun,

08:50.020 --> 08:51.260
it's over between us.

08:57.000 --> 08:57.630
Chu,

08:58.510 --> 09:00.200
we've faced death together,

09:00.790 --> 09:02.390
sharing both joy and sorrow.

09:03.000 --> 09:04.200
I don't believe there's anything

09:04.200 --> 09:06.130
between us that can't be resolved.

09:06.870 --> 09:08.530
Why are you being so resolute?

09:08.790 --> 09:09.510
Yan Xun,

09:09.700 --> 09:11.230
we used to walk side by side,

09:11.840 --> 09:14.390
and we were each other's only comrades
and family.

09:14.390 --> 09:15.240
The path we once walked

09:15.240 --> 09:16.670
has already come to an end.

09:16.670 --> 09:17.630
Look behind.

09:18.550 --> 09:20.750
We've long since gone our separate ways.

09:20.750 --> 09:21.750
I was born a slave,

09:22.120 --> 09:24.240
with only one goal in mind—
to abolish slavery and stop the wars,

09:24.240 --> 09:25.960
so that even those with lives
as worthless as grass

09:25.960 --> 09:27.560
could have the right to live.

09:27.810 --> 09:30.200
But all that remains in your eyes
is revenge.

09:30.200 --> 09:31.720
You want to use fresh blood

09:31.720 --> 09:33.150
to wash away the hatred of your family

09:33.150 --> 09:34.320
and Great Yan.

09:34.320 --> 09:35.150
Chu,

09:36.500 --> 09:39.120
this world is inherently
a survival of the fittest.

09:39.120 --> 09:41.360
There's never been such a thing
as justice or fairness.

09:41.360 --> 09:42.490
There was no justice

09:42.790 --> 09:44.360
when the Yan clan perished tragically

09:44.360 --> 09:45.490
at Jiuyou Platform.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.870
When we were imprisoned
in the Yingge Courtyard,

09:47.870 --> 09:48.720
with no one to depend on,

09:48.720 --> 09:49.980
no one was there for us.

09:50.750 --> 09:53.390
When I lost everything and was in despair,

09:54.010 --> 09:55.410
the only person by my side

09:56.130 --> 09:57.210
was you.

09:59.200 --> 09:59.870
Chu,

10:01.270 --> 10:02.150
to me,

10:03.390 --> 10:04.120
the world

10:05.390 --> 10:06.150
and justice

10:07.800 --> 10:10.200
are nothing compared
to the bond between us.

10:10.200 --> 10:10.870
Yan Xun.

10:11.640 --> 10:12.470
I was wrong.

10:13.150 --> 10:15.150
I thought we shared the same ideals.

10:15.360 --> 10:17.320
Because we depended on each other so much,

10:17.320 --> 10:19.270
I saw you as my closest person.

10:20.080 --> 10:22.210
But now we no longer walk the same path.

10:23.200 --> 10:24.730
Please, let go of yourself,

10:25.390 --> 10:26.600
and let go of me.

10:47.200 --> 10:48.000
Chu.

10:49.790 --> 10:51.120
I can guarantee that,

10:53.630 --> 10:54.750
on your own,

10:56.230 --> 10:58.360
you won't be able to fight your way out.

11:15.670 --> 11:16.600
Zhuge Yue?

11:16.960 --> 11:17.600
Yan Xun,

11:18.480 --> 11:20.480
I didn't expect us to meet like this.

11:21.440 --> 11:22.080
Xing.

11:22.750 --> 11:23.810
You said yesterday

11:24.200 --> 11:25.670
that you wanted me
to stay by your side forever.

11:25.670 --> 11:26.590
I promise you.

11:27.390 --> 11:29.590
I want you to stay by my side forever too.

11:29.630 --> 11:30.960
To the ends of the earth,

11:31.750 --> 11:33.150
we live and die together.

11:34.430 --> 11:35.430
Zhuge Yue.

11:38.320 --> 11:40.980
You shot an arrow at me
outside Zhenhuangcheng.

11:41.440 --> 11:43.200
I paid you back at the frozen lake.

11:43.200 --> 11:44.440
Now we are even.

11:44.910 --> 11:46.320
If you leave now

11:46.840 --> 11:49.100
and stop interfering between Chu and me,

11:49.790 --> 11:51.840
I can pretend you were never here.

11:52.360 --> 11:55.020
What happened between us
can be left in the past,

11:55.630 --> 11:57.600
but if you persist in your ways,

11:58.510 --> 11:59.750
even your father...

11:59.750 --> 12:00.630
Shut up!

12:01.870 --> 12:04.080
You have no right to judge my father!

12:04.360 --> 12:05.620
Attention, everyone!

12:05.870 --> 12:07.800
Whoever brings me Zhuge Yue's head

12:08.720 --> 12:10.150
will be made
a Marquis of a Thousand Households!

12:10.150 --> 12:10.960
Yes!

12:34.590 --> 12:35.320
Let's go!

12:39.440 --> 12:40.050
Retreat!

12:54.600 --> 12:56.960
His Majesty is wise and brave.

12:57.300 --> 12:59.700
He is the one chosen by the gods
of Great Yan.

12:59.840 --> 13:00.390
Yes.

13:00.840 --> 13:01.630
I knew it.

13:01.870 --> 13:02.480
Under the guise

13:02.480 --> 13:04.480
of a prisoner exchange, His Majesty

13:04.510 --> 13:05.790
captured Lincheng

13:06.200 --> 13:08.360
and completely deceived
those from Great Yong.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.510
Soon, we'll be able

13:09.630 --> 13:11.720
to march all the way to Zhenhuangcheng

13:11.720 --> 13:14.120
and avenge our fallen brothers.

13:14.120 --> 13:15.720
Yes, avenge them!

13:17.670 --> 13:18.320
Come on!

13:23.630 --> 13:24.960
Let's raise our glasses

13:26.200 --> 13:27.550
to Great Yan

13:28.720 --> 13:29.650
and our new King!

13:29.840 --> 13:31.240
To His Majesty!

14:01.320 --> 14:02.120
Your Majesty.

14:02.800 --> 14:05.630
I heard you led the Black Eagle Army
and took Lincheng.

14:05.630 --> 14:06.720
I'm here to congratulate you

14:06.720 --> 14:07.750
and Great Yan.

14:12.790 --> 14:14.240
We won a great victory at Lincheng.

14:14.240 --> 14:17.150
Your Majesty, why aren't you celebrating
with the soldiers?

14:17.150 --> 14:18.720
Did you see Chu?

14:19.440 --> 14:20.110
What?

14:20.720 --> 14:21.750
I saw her.

14:23.630 --> 14:25.090
She also came to Lincheng.

14:25.370 --> 14:27.080
She rescued He Xiao.

14:28.080 --> 14:29.540
Your Majesty, you saw her?

14:29.720 --> 14:31.320
If you see her next time,

14:32.030 --> 14:33.750
bring her back to me.

14:35.320 --> 14:37.250
If she can't be brought back alive,

14:39.080 --> 14:40.360
dead is fine.

14:40.840 --> 14:41.640
Your Majesty.

14:43.790 --> 14:45.790
Haven't you always wanted her dead?

15:04.390 --> 15:05.790
It should be fine, right?

15:06.840 --> 15:07.510
It...

15:08.630 --> 15:09.790
It should be fine.

15:10.910 --> 15:11.790
Should?

15:12.510 --> 15:13.550
You think I don't know?

15:13.550 --> 15:15.510
An hour after taking the Huiyuan Pill,

15:15.510 --> 15:16.550
one's vital energy is restored,

15:16.550 --> 15:17.720
but it shortens lifespan.

15:17.720 --> 15:19.120
And you tell me it should be fine?

15:19.120 --> 15:19.650
Don't...

15:20.600 --> 15:21.390
Don't blame me.

15:21.390 --> 15:22.240
It was Young Master Zhuge who insisted...

15:22.240 --> 15:22.840
Xing.

15:23.270 --> 15:24.320
I forced him.

15:24.780 --> 15:26.380
I had to save you at that time.

15:28.440 --> 15:29.120
Xing!

15:40.910 --> 15:41.600
Xing.

15:42.360 --> 15:43.000
It's me.

15:45.030 --> 15:46.270
What do you want?

15:47.120 --> 15:48.150
I came to tell you

15:49.080 --> 15:51.270
everything that's happened
during all this time.

15:51.270 --> 15:52.870
I don't want to know anymore.

15:53.220 --> 15:53.980
Leave.

16:18.380 --> 16:18.970
Come on.

16:22.790 --> 16:23.720
I never thought

16:24.200 --> 16:25.360
I'd still be alive

16:25.360 --> 16:26.720
to drink such fine wine.

16:26.870 --> 16:28.390
After Young Master
fell into the frozen lake,

16:28.390 --> 16:31.120
Qingshan Manor sent us Moon Guards
to the front line.

16:31.120 --> 16:33.050
Some of us died, some were injured,

16:33.720 --> 16:35.850
and those captured suffered greatly.

16:37.200 --> 16:38.460
Who would have thought

16:38.630 --> 16:40.270
we'd see the Young Master again

16:40.270 --> 16:42.990
and be here alive,
eating meat and drinking wine?

16:42.990 --> 16:43.870
To us being alive.

16:43.870 --> 16:44.330
Cheers.

16:50.460 --> 16:51.460
How can you be here

16:51.480 --> 16:53.480
drinking such fine wine without me?

16:54.150 --> 16:55.270
How did you do it?

16:55.670 --> 16:56.670
I didn't even notice,

16:56.670 --> 16:58.600
and the glass is already in your hand.

16:58.600 --> 17:00.200
I just witnessed it.

17:00.480 --> 17:02.670
Miss Fang's nickname is "Master Thief."

17:02.670 --> 17:05.069
Looks like there's nothing she can't take.

17:05.920 --> 17:06.480
You...

17:11.109 --> 17:11.839
Tastes good.

17:15.349 --> 17:16.790
This is what happened

17:16.790 --> 17:18.310
after I fell into the frozen lake.

17:18.310 --> 17:19.770
I was saved by King Ximeng,

17:20.030 --> 17:21.640
took the deadly poison Blood on Snow,

17:21.640 --> 17:22.900
and became his shadow.

17:23.550 --> 17:25.280
I promised to do 3 things for him

17:25.880 --> 17:27.540
in exchange for the antidote.

17:34.070 --> 17:34.920
Zhuge Yue,

17:36.680 --> 17:38.680
why are you only telling me this now?

17:45.510 --> 17:46.510
Are you mute?

17:47.110 --> 17:48.770
Why are you only saying it now?

17:49.440 --> 17:52.030
Tell me! Why?

17:52.310 --> 17:53.880
Why? Why?

18:10.450 --> 18:12.940
Zhuge Yue, promise me

18:13.920 --> 18:16.270
that from now on, you won't hide
anything from me anymore,

18:16.270 --> 18:18.270
and you won't avoid me.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.360
Did you hear me?

18:30.670 --> 18:31.470
Remember,

18:32.420 --> 18:34.750
you are not allowed
to hide anything from me anymore.

18:34.750 --> 18:36.400
Considering your injuries,

18:37.710 --> 18:39.170
I will let you go this time.

18:53.680 --> 18:54.540
Your Highness.

18:55.590 --> 18:56.110
I...

18:57.440 --> 18:58.570
Young Master Zhuge!

18:59.240 --> 19:00.310
I went through a great deal of trouble

19:00.310 --> 19:01.480
to save your life.

19:01.480 --> 19:03.030
At the very least,
you should follow medical advice—

19:03.030 --> 19:06.090
no alcohol, no intimacy,
and avoid meat and heavy food.

19:07.240 --> 19:07.830
This...

19:13.080 --> 19:16.660
[Zhuge Yue] [Yan Xun] [Li Ce]

19:20.240 --> 19:21.500
You don't understand.

19:21.680 --> 19:23.480
Yan Xun and Her Highness
have known each other since childhood

19:23.480 --> 19:25.030
and have gone through many hardships
together.

19:25.030 --> 19:26.590
Even though they have now
turned against each other,

19:26.590 --> 19:28.750
the scar in Her Highness's heart
is still there.

19:28.750 --> 19:29.880
She can't forget him even if she wants to.

19:29.880 --> 19:31.790
If Yan Xun keeps pushing like this,

19:31.790 --> 19:33.400
the embers could easily reignite.

19:33.400 --> 19:34.240
If you ask me,

19:34.240 --> 19:36.030
our princess will eventually
return to Great Yan

19:36.030 --> 19:37.430
as its princess consort.

19:38.190 --> 19:39.460
She's not stupid.

19:39.750 --> 19:41.480
Why would she go to a desolate place
like Great Yan

19:41.480 --> 19:42.440
to be a princess consort?

19:42.440 --> 19:45.160
It's better for her to stay in Biantang
and be the Crown Princess.

19:45.160 --> 19:47.920
Our Crown Prince is wealthy
and quite romantic.

19:47.920 --> 19:49.210
She has suffered so much before.

19:49.210 --> 19:51.830
Only by staying with him
can she live a good life.

19:51.830 --> 19:52.720
What do you think?

19:52.720 --> 19:53.480
What do you think?

19:53.480 --> 19:55.160
I... I choose Zhuge Yue.

19:55.270 --> 19:56.110
I think

19:56.110 --> 19:58.590
Miss Xing will definitely choose our boss.

19:58.590 --> 19:59.550
Why Zhuge Yue?

19:59.550 --> 20:02.350
Because our boss
is both talented and handsome.

20:02.350 --> 20:03.270
Yue Shiyi,

20:03.440 --> 20:04.880
your boss is not even here.

20:04.880 --> 20:06.740
Why are you still flattering him?

20:06.790 --> 20:07.590
Be honest,

20:07.680 --> 20:09.310
who are you really betting on?

20:09.310 --> 20:09.800
I...

20:09.830 --> 20:12.150
You've left out an option in this bet.

20:13.270 --> 20:14.310
I saw everything.

20:20.240 --> 20:21.400
I bet on the fourth one.

20:21.400 --> 20:22.750
The fourth option?

20:22.750 --> 20:24.960
Xing will not be anyone's
princess consort.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.510
She will only be herself.

20:30.680 --> 20:31.790
Why do I feel like

20:31.790 --> 20:33.480
he's cursing our princess

20:33.640 --> 20:35.700
to stay unmarried for her whole life?

21:02.400 --> 21:03.200
Lady Chu,

21:03.480 --> 21:04.960
it's so dusty outside.

21:05.200 --> 21:06.840
We'd better close the window

21:06.870 --> 21:08.830
so the dust won't come in.

21:10.720 --> 21:11.350
Stop!

21:18.270 --> 21:19.030
General Chu.

21:19.870 --> 21:22.390
I'm getting a bit tired riding.

21:22.750 --> 21:24.200
And the scenery here is not bad.

21:24.200 --> 21:25.920
How about we switch?

21:28.200 --> 21:28.790
Sure.

21:29.030 --> 21:30.200
I was just feeling a bit stuffy.

21:30.200 --> 21:31.160
Let's switch.

21:35.070 --> 21:36.270
I get carsick easily.

21:36.510 --> 21:38.030
What do you mean, Yue Shiyi?

21:38.030 --> 21:39.490
-Don't meddle.
-Alright.

21:39.880 --> 21:41.680
Yue Shiyi, Fang Miaomiao,
get in the carriage.

21:41.680 --> 21:42.880
I will ride the horse.

22:15.030 --> 22:16.270
Don't you think

22:16.910 --> 22:19.110
Zhan Ziyu has been a bit strange lately?

22:19.160 --> 22:20.780
Ever since the incident at the inn,

22:20.780 --> 22:22.440
he hasn't caused any trouble.

22:22.830 --> 22:25.090
He doesn't even come near our carriages.

22:25.550 --> 22:27.000
Isn't that a good thing, Your Highness?

22:27.000 --> 22:28.990
Didn't he buy an eagle for a high price?

22:28.990 --> 22:30.720
He's been playing with it all the time.

22:30.720 --> 22:31.440
I think

22:31.720 --> 22:34.720
he was probably
scared out of his wits by you last time.

22:35.880 --> 22:38.640
I don't think it's that simple.

22:39.070 --> 22:40.240
Rest assured, Your Highness.

22:40.240 --> 22:42.270
We will arrive in Tangjing
in the blink of an eye.

22:42.270 --> 22:43.680
As long as we enter the city safely,

22:43.680 --> 22:45.060
this hurdle will be behind us.

22:45.060 --> 22:47.510
No matter how he tries to cause trouble,
it won't work.

22:47.510 --> 22:49.130
[Tangjing]

22:53.720 --> 22:54.550
Slow down.

23:02.270 --> 23:03.200
Your Highness.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.860
Since you have returned safely
from this trip,

23:06.860 --> 23:09.120
I will now return to the palace to report.

23:09.160 --> 23:10.820
I won't disturb Your Highness

23:11.680 --> 23:13.550
and your distinguished guests any further.

23:13.550 --> 23:15.750
Thank you for your hard work, Lord Zhan.

23:25.050 --> 23:27.990
Give this to Lord Yu of the Ministry of Personnel's
Supervisory Department.

23:27.990 --> 23:29.850
Tell him it's Her Majesty's will.

23:30.180 --> 23:30.730
Yes.

23:35.240 --> 23:37.480
I came especially to thank Her Majesty

23:37.480 --> 23:39.700
for arranging the marriage
between the Prince of Luo and me.

23:39.700 --> 23:41.480
[Linrui Palace]

23:39.790 --> 23:41.450
Please wait a moment, My Lady.

23:41.550 --> 23:42.680
Beauty Hu is inside

23:42.680 --> 23:44.270
paying her respects to Her Majesty.

23:44.270 --> 23:46.270
I will go and announce your arrival.

23:55.060 --> 23:57.090
[Beauty Hu]

24:07.440 --> 24:08.510
Let her in.

24:13.990 --> 24:16.990
You must be the girl
the Prince of Luo is about to marry.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.900
Your Highness, you are...

24:20.200 --> 24:21.680
It doesn't matter if you don't know me.

24:21.680 --> 24:23.030
I know you.

24:23.440 --> 24:26.240
You are the famous Princess Chun'er
of Great Yong,

24:26.250 --> 24:29.180
who almost married the new King
of Great Yan, Yan Xun.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.000
Pardon me.

24:32.120 --> 24:34.180
I shouldn't have touched a sore spot.

24:34.510 --> 24:35.750
But it's all good now.

24:36.320 --> 24:39.440
You will soon be the Princess Consort of Luo
in our Biantang.

24:39.440 --> 24:42.040
However, there is one thing
that surprises me.

24:42.160 --> 24:43.790
You don't look...

24:44.190 --> 24:46.700
like Princess Fu at all.

24:46.890 --> 24:50.240
The Prince of Luo has been deeply in love
with Princess Fu for years.

24:50.240 --> 24:52.120
Why did he suddenly
have a change of heart?

24:52.120 --> 24:53.050
What did you say?

24:54.540 --> 24:56.140
Don't tell me you don't know.

24:56.240 --> 24:59.100
The Prince of Luo and Princess Fu
were once engaged.

24:59.240 --> 25:02.490
The Prince of Luo has remained unmarried
for years because of Princess Fu.

25:02.490 --> 25:05.170
Now that Princess Fu
has been brought back,

25:05.640 --> 25:07.030
we all thought

25:07.030 --> 25:10.560
the Prince of Luo would resume
his engagement with Princess Fu.

25:10.750 --> 25:12.440
Is the Princess Fu you're talking about

25:12.440 --> 25:14.570
the one in the Crown Prince's Mansion?

25:14.750 --> 25:17.010
The Prince of Luo was once engaged to her?

25:17.680 --> 25:18.480
Beauty Hu.

25:19.350 --> 25:20.080
Her Majesty?

25:25.310 --> 25:26.350
Your Majesty.

25:27.400 --> 25:28.110
Come here.

25:33.720 --> 25:34.960
What did you just say?

25:35.400 --> 25:36.200
Your Majesty,

25:36.350 --> 25:36.880
I...

25:41.030 --> 25:42.000
Your Majesty,

25:42.190 --> 25:43.560
I was wrong.

25:43.640 --> 25:44.310
Servants.

25:44.960 --> 25:46.830
Beauty Hu has behaved improperly
in words and actions

25:46.830 --> 25:48.110
and slandered a prince.

25:48.110 --> 25:49.640
According to palace rules,

25:49.850 --> 25:51.280
slap her 20 times.

25:51.680 --> 25:52.680
Your Majesty,

25:53.110 --> 25:54.350
I was wrong!

25:54.680 --> 25:55.790
Your Majesty,

25:56.110 --> 25:57.400
I was wrong!

25:57.750 --> 25:59.350
Please forgive me!

25:59.350 --> 26:00.750
Your Majesty!

26:01.110 --> 26:02.830
Your Majesty!

26:40.190 --> 26:41.190
How could this be?

26:42.110 --> 26:42.830
Chun'er!

26:45.920 --> 26:46.590
Chun'er.

26:47.430 --> 26:48.400
You misunderstood.

26:48.400 --> 26:49.070
This portrait is...

26:49.070 --> 26:50.590
It's Princess Fu in this portrait.

26:50.590 --> 26:52.650
You were engaged to her, weren't you?

26:54.720 --> 26:55.850
Then do you know that

26:56.220 --> 26:58.490
the Princess Fu in the Crown Prince's Mansion
is an impostor,

26:58.490 --> 27:01.350
and that she is Chu Qiao,
a convicted slave from Great Yong?

27:01.350 --> 27:02.160
I know.

27:02.830 --> 27:04.520
Her Majesty had suspected it long ago

27:04.520 --> 27:06.180
and called me to identify her.

27:06.350 --> 27:09.790
She and the Crown Prince
privately asked me to help cover it up.

27:09.790 --> 27:12.390
You actually testified
for a convicted slave?

27:12.400 --> 27:13.030
Yes.

27:15.830 --> 27:19.030
So you like Princess Fu.

27:19.310 --> 27:21.440
And because she looks like Princess Fu,

27:21.440 --> 27:22.790
you like her too,

27:24.030 --> 27:24.960
don't you?

27:25.350 --> 27:26.160
No, Chun'er.

27:26.240 --> 27:27.030
I don't.

27:27.890 --> 27:29.130
I did like Fu before,

27:29.550 --> 27:30.750
but I know very well that she is not...

27:30.750 --> 27:31.790
Then burn it!

27:42.330 --> 27:44.160
You claim that you like me!

27:44.190 --> 27:45.470
You liar!

27:46.240 --> 27:46.850
Li Yan,

27:47.350 --> 27:48.680
you don't have to love me.

27:48.680 --> 27:50.880
You can have someone else in your heart,

27:51.000 --> 27:52.480
but it can't be her.

27:52.510 --> 27:53.880
It can't be Chu Qiao!

28:07.010 --> 28:08.640
My Lady, your wedding is coming up soon.

28:08.640 --> 28:09.790
The crowd here is quite mixed.

28:09.790 --> 28:11.070
We should head back early,

28:11.070 --> 28:12.680
or His Highness will be worried.

28:12.680 --> 28:13.590
Why go back?

28:13.670 --> 28:15.000
He won't worry about me.

28:15.830 --> 28:17.270
I'm just a substitute.

28:17.410 --> 28:19.540
The person in his heart is Princess Fu.

28:19.680 --> 28:21.240
Your Highness,
you shouldn't think like that.

28:21.240 --> 28:22.680
Since His Highness met you,

28:22.680 --> 28:24.610
he has changed a lot.

28:26.680 --> 28:27.880
Miss, have you seen this person?

28:27.880 --> 28:28.680
No.

28:29.270 --> 28:30.130
I'll take this.

28:31.920 --> 28:32.400
Miss,

28:32.400 --> 28:33.800
have you seen this woman?

28:39.450 --> 28:42.740
[Prince of Luo's Mansion]

29:05.170 --> 29:06.900
Your Highness! Your Highness!

29:07.640 --> 29:08.500
Your Highness,

29:08.640 --> 29:10.070
this is the nuptial wine
for you and His Highness.

29:10.070 --> 29:12.000
You can't drink it all by yourself.

29:12.000 --> 29:13.200
I want more!

29:13.680 --> 29:14.750
Bring more wine!

29:15.720 --> 29:17.270
Your Highness, you are really drunk.

29:17.270 --> 29:18.670
You can't drink anymore.

29:22.920 --> 29:23.780
Your Highness,

29:23.880 --> 29:26.030
this wedding fan can only be removed
when His Highness comes.

29:26.030 --> 29:27.960
Otherwise it would bring bad luck.

29:30.590 --> 29:31.400
Chunxing.

29:33.570 --> 29:37.090
Do you know how many times
I've been married?

29:39.200 --> 29:40.000
Three times.

29:41.070 --> 29:42.740
This is the 3rd time.

29:45.160 --> 29:48.950
The first time, on my wedding day,

29:49.030 --> 29:50.920
snow was falling heavily.

29:51.720 --> 29:56.720
My groom rebelled
and led troops against my father.

29:57.350 --> 29:58.270
I begged him,

29:59.550 --> 30:01.000
but he wouldn't listen.

30:02.860 --> 30:06.050
Instead, he threw the wedding robe
I made for him

30:06.080 --> 30:07.320
onto the ground,

30:09.120 --> 30:11.990
letting horses trample over it.

30:13.200 --> 30:14.060
Your Highness!

30:17.180 --> 30:19.180
He walked past me so coldly,

30:19.210 --> 30:21.450
so decisively.

30:22.240 --> 30:23.850
He walked past my body

30:24.680 --> 30:26.290
and shattered my heart.

30:27.750 --> 30:28.750
The second time,

30:30.680 --> 30:31.830
I carefully arranged

30:31.830 --> 30:35.070
a fake wedding for myself.

30:38.810 --> 30:40.870
Your Highness, you are really drunk.

30:41.030 --> 30:41.590
Here.

30:42.440 --> 30:43.030
Here.

30:49.310 --> 30:50.000
Chunxing.

30:51.350 --> 30:52.310
You know what?

30:53.750 --> 30:55.480
I finally got married.

31:32.570 --> 31:34.970
What else is there for me
to look forward to?

31:41.960 --> 31:43.490
Your Highness, be careful!

31:46.550 --> 31:48.150
Your Highness, your foot...

31:49.160 --> 31:49.750
Chun'er!

31:51.700 --> 31:53.270
Chun'er, are you alright?

32:25.350 --> 32:25.960
Chun'er.

32:27.120 --> 32:29.070
If you don't want to get married yet,

32:29.070 --> 32:31.550
we can pretend
today's wedding never happened.

32:31.550 --> 32:33.010
I can keep waiting for you,

32:33.400 --> 32:35.200
until you fall in love with me,

32:36.310 --> 32:38.570
until the day
you truly want to be my wife.

33:03.830 --> 33:05.590
I heard Her Majesty likes jade,

33:05.830 --> 33:07.400
so I specially found a fine piece.

33:07.400 --> 33:09.080
Her Majesty is not in the palace.

33:09.080 --> 33:13.210
Princess Consort of Luo, please follow me
to the hall and wait for a moment.

33:21.160 --> 33:23.220
Your Highness, please have some tea.

33:26.460 --> 33:28.250
[Qifeng Palace]

33:35.620 --> 33:37.850
I have already handed the evidence
obtained from the trip to Qiongzhou

33:37.850 --> 33:39.550
to Lord Yu of the Ministry of Personnel.

33:39.550 --> 33:41.270
That King Ximeng is a fake.

33:41.680 --> 33:43.000
He was sent by Ximeng to Biantang

33:43.000 --> 33:45.290
to obtain Director Zhang's
manufacturing compendium.

33:45.290 --> 33:47.010
I just don't know how he

33:47.040 --> 33:49.040
got involved with the Crown Prince.

33:51.400 --> 33:53.880
This son of mine is quite something.

33:54.680 --> 33:56.790
I really underestimated him.

33:57.000 --> 33:58.260
There is another thing

33:58.510 --> 34:00.200
that I also find very strange.

34:01.200 --> 34:02.000
What is it?

34:02.020 --> 34:04.640
In the team
of the Crown Prince and Ximeng this time,

34:04.640 --> 34:06.240
I didn't see Princess Fu,

34:06.480 --> 34:07.610
that Chu Qiao.

34:08.190 --> 34:09.440
And as far as I know,

34:09.850 --> 34:11.469
she is not
in the Crown Prince's Mansion either.

34:11.469 --> 34:14.030
Are you saying Chu Qiao is missing?

34:15.030 --> 34:15.670
Yes.

34:17.020 --> 34:19.310
I worry she will affect our grand plan.

34:25.639 --> 34:27.889
Then let's strike first

34:28.360 --> 34:29.440
and do it quickly

34:30.400 --> 34:32.070
to avoid any complications.

34:32.600 --> 34:33.590
As long as we solidify

34:33.590 --> 34:37.170
the Crown Prince's charges of treason
and collusion with the enemy,

34:37.170 --> 34:38.730
even 10 Chu Qiaos

34:39.360 --> 34:40.760
won't be able to save him.

34:46.429 --> 34:48.949
Today is the 6th, right?

34:56.030 --> 34:57.110
Today is the 6th.

34:57.400 --> 34:58.920
Are the carriages ready?

34:59.470 --> 35:00.320
Your Majesty,

35:00.400 --> 35:02.400
the carriages are ready outside.

35:02.920 --> 35:04.360
But today is the Greater Heat.

35:04.360 --> 35:06.150
For years, you've gone to chant sutras

35:06.150 --> 35:08.880
for Crown Prince Maocheng
on the sixth of every month.

35:08.880 --> 35:11.010
But it's exceptionally hot this year.

35:11.320 --> 35:12.630
I'm afraid your body

35:12.630 --> 35:13.960
can't handle the journey.

35:13.960 --> 35:14.630
It's fine.

35:14.840 --> 35:16.550
Let's go to Tianlong Temple.

35:16.670 --> 35:17.630
Your Majesty!

35:20.960 --> 35:21.670
Your Majesty!

35:21.670 --> 35:23.800
I have something important to report!

35:24.070 --> 35:26.000
Don't you know what day it is today?

35:26.670 --> 35:29.150
Rushing into the palace so recklessly.

35:32.590 --> 35:33.190
Beauty,

35:33.480 --> 35:35.010
what happened to your face?

35:36.960 --> 35:37.760
Your Majesty,

35:37.960 --> 35:39.480
I know very well

35:39.480 --> 35:41.880
that today is the day
you go to Tianlong Temple

35:41.880 --> 35:44.280
to chant sutras for Crown Prince Maocheng.

35:44.360 --> 35:46.550
Your devotion
is known to the heavens and the earth.

35:46.550 --> 35:47.960
But do you know

35:47.960 --> 35:49.480
what Her Majesty has been doing

35:49.480 --> 35:51.070
every time you're away?

35:53.760 --> 35:54.800
What do you mean?

36:05.840 --> 36:06.910
Greetings, Your Majesty!

36:06.910 --> 36:08.180
Greetings, Beauty Hu!

36:16.010 --> 36:18.270
Where is the Empress? Why isn't she here?

36:19.400 --> 36:20.260
Her Majesty...

36:20.480 --> 36:21.810
Her Majesty is resting.

36:24.070 --> 36:25.130
You lowly servant!

36:56.070 --> 36:56.760
Empress.

36:57.620 --> 36:59.870
What are you two women doing?

37:00.070 --> 37:00.630
I...

37:01.880 --> 37:04.340
I'm keeping Her Majesty company
in the bath.

37:41.690 --> 37:43.160
Today isn't a festival.

37:43.400 --> 37:45.060
Why did you release so many sky lanterns?

37:45.060 --> 37:45.910
Zhuge Yue,

37:46.670 --> 37:47.800
what's your plan?

37:50.000 --> 37:51.400
I will never willingly

37:51.400 --> 37:52.960
an incompetent coward!

37:53.070 --> 37:53.840
I am not!

37:56.480 --> 37:57.540
Her Majesty orders

37:57.760 --> 37:59.760
that the Queen of Lingyue
and the false King Ximeng

37:59.760 --> 38:01.000
be arrested immediately!

38:01.000 --> 38:02.360
Since you have moved on,

38:02.860 --> 38:04.420
how could I be dwelling on it?
